            "body": "It's the quickstart, which is not the place to justify the existence of things. See the docs about the CLI for a long list of all the things it can do.\r\n\r\nThe environment variable is required due to how things work internally. I don't find it cumbersome. The CLI docs document multiple ways to automate setting it. You're welcome to submit a PR to add it as a CLI option. See #2292 for a summary.\r\n\r\nThe final section in the quickstart you linked to refers you to the documentation on deploying."
