            "body": "Ok, thank you for the pointers.\r\n\r\nThis documentation for why the flask executable is recommended over app.run can be found at \r\n - http://flask.pocoo.org/docs/1.0/server/#server\r\n\r\nIn addition some other reasons are given at\r\n- https://github.com/pallets/flask/issues/1575#issuecomment-147103623\r\n- https://github.com/pallets/flask/issues/1575#issuecomment-147116830\r\n\r\nThe documentation of the CLI (including the non-trivial integration into the PyCharm IDE) can be found at\r\n- http://flask.pocoo.org/docs/1.0/cli/\r\n\r\nHope that helps anyone who is coming from an older version of Flask"
